{
  "chapter": 4,
  "chapter_summary": "第四章围绕五龙亭展开多线战斗。康劫生趁众人观战之际暗杀萧秋水，被潮阳疯女阻止。大肚和尚与血影大师激战，双方各施绝技——不不拳对大开碑手、肚皮神功对火焰刀与铁头功，最终平分秋色。屈寒山以“大侠”身份到场，巧舌如簧地操纵广东五虎，使他们误信萧秋水是权力帮中人而放弃相助。左常生步步逼近欲杀萧秋水，大肚和尚挺身为友，甘愿以命相随。千钧一发之际，大侠梁斗赶到，轻松化解血影大师攻势。萧秋水当众揭发屈寒山即是权力帮“剑王”。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_chao_yang_feng_nv",
      "speaker_name": "潮阳疯女",
      "listener": "char_kang_jie_sheng",
      "text": "“我早留意你要做什么了，你要不要再做一次试试看？”",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“少林铁头功！”",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chao_yang_feng_nv",
      "speaker_name": "疯女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“喂，你们三人可一齐来，合攻我看看，包准每一个都手忙脚乱，绝无冷常”",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_chao_yang_feng_nv",
      "text": "“刘女侠今天兴致怎地这么高？”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“误会、误会！这是一场误会！”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "speaker_name": "罗海牛",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“误会？怎么会是误会？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“广东五虎，行侠仗义，名闻江湖，但是诸位一定误会这几位是权力帮中人了！”",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_cai",
      "speaker_name": "吴财",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“我们也不清楚。这位鸟鸟大师是我们的好朋友，他见这位朋友被挟持，便要出手相救，我们也过来帮忙，动手之下，才从武功中得知这几位……几位似……是权力帮中的血影大师、盛江北、左常生等人，所以才打出了真火……”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“几位义勇过人，这点老夫自是佩服，只是……”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“诸侠年轻有为，血气方刚，有时不免卷入无谓纷争……”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_shui",
      "speaker_name": "阿水",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“难道他们不是权力帮中的‘九天十地，十九人魔’中人？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“若是权力帮中人，老夫会为他们说话么？！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "speaker_name": "罗海牛、吴财、杀仔",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“屈大侠德高望重，谁人不服？屈大侠一言九鼎，我等自是信服，此事……怕是我们真的……弄错了。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“不但弄错了，而且是弄拧了”",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“这些人都是矢志要歼灭权力帮忠义之士，”",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“他才是叛徒！”",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“好险啊好险！”",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_cai",
      "speaker_name": "吴财",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“屈大侠明示。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“差点为虎作伥，荡尽了广东五虎赫世英名！”",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_zai",
      "speaker_name": "杀仔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我们不知此人是权力帮中人，帮错了他！”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_cai",
      "speaker_name": "吴财",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“既有屈大侠指示，我们不插手便是。”",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_shui",
      "speaker_name": "阿水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“本来我们和这小兄弟也蛮投缘，怎料……”",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "speaker_name": "罗海牛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“幸有屈大侠明示，才不致闹出笑话。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chao_yang_feng_nv",
      "speaker_name": "疯女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“谁是权力帮的败类，我们可不晓得，但屈大侠却是我们所佩服的前辈，这次我们就听了屈大侠的话，鸟乌，此事我们不管了。”",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“谎话！他在撒谎！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_chang_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "左常生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“你们可曾听说过屈寒山屈大侠也说谎言？”",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "speaker_name": "钟无离",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“这小子有眼无珠！”",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_you_kong",
      "speaker_name": "柳有孔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“一口废话，最好充耳不闻！”",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_jie_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "康劫生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“此人该死。”",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“此人该死！”",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "大肚和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“有我在！你们动他，我就拼了！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "text": "“少林大渡？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "大肚和尚",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“是！”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "text": "“少林我上过两次，达摩堂的十龙僧人，跟我很熟，”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "text": "“你是给达摩堂逐出少林吗？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "大肚和尚",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“是。”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "text": "“少林寺真是习武的好地方，而且武艺繁精，穷其一生也练不完，你何不留在少林继续学武？”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "大肚和尚",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“少林是从不收容被逐出的弟子。”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "text": "“或者，我可以替你说几句话。”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "大肚和尚",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“谢谢。不过，与其在少林替我讲情，不如，烦劳屈大侠，在这儿替我这位兄弟说情还好。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "text": "“你知道他是谁？！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "大肚和尚",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“萧秋水。”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "text": "“你知道他犯了什么事？！”",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "大肚和尚",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“不知道。”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "text": "“你什么都不知道，还敢帮他？！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "大肚和尚",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“是。”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "text": "“为什么？！”",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "大肚和尚",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“因为今日如我俩调换位置，他一样会帮我的。”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "text": "“要是他作的是十恶不赦的事呢？！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "大肚和尚",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“萧秋水不会作十恶不赦的事！”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "text": "“我告诉你，他现在所做的正是该打下十八层地狱的事！”",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "大肚和尚",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“阿弥陀佛。那我也跟着去，何况我不入地狱，谁入地狱？”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“那你就入地狱好了。”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ying_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "血影大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“挡我者死！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "大肚和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“死者不生！”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“怎么啦？你穴道解了。”",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“梁大侠！”",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "text": "“要见这位大渡，传一句话，东海惠州林公子不来了，他要我转告大渡这句话。”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“梁大侠，他，他就是‘权力帮’中‘剑王’！”",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 4
    }
  ],
